manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Freshen the air in the car Put this air outlet perfume on the air vent in the car. When you turn on the air conditioner in the car, the fragrance of the essential oil will also drift out with the wind of the air conditioner. This is a fresh and natural smell, which can remove the car. The odor in the car will give you a comfortable interior environment, and it is very friendly to people with motion sickness. When you feel tired after driving for a long time, smelling this smell can drive away the tiredness, make you feel relaxed, restore energy and maintain a good state.

This essential oil diffuser for use at home gives you fresh air and a wonderful feeling When you take a break from work at home, place the diffuser over the vent of a fan or air conditioner, the smell of essential oil will become more intense, making the air in the room more fresh, and you will feel very pleasant and comfortable when you smell this scent. The charming smell will make you more focused and happy. It is an essential essential oil perfume diffuser in your home.

Air conditioner vent clip fresh air This exhaust clip can also be placed at the air outlet of the air conditioner at home. The cool air of the air conditioner is accompanied by the fresh and delicious aroma of essential oils, making the whole room full of fragrance. You can do anything and you will feel comfortable physically and mentally, allowing you to Calm and relaxing, it is a must-have air freshener for the home.

The scent spreads out fast There are many small holes at the bottom of our air outlet perfume clip, and the metal cover is a hollow pattern of natural tree of life. This design can make the essential oil fragrance on the sponge pad diffuse faster, enhance the fragrance, better fresh air, and enhance comfort sense.

Small and exquisite This round tuyere clip is 1.18 inches in diameter, the bottom clip is 1.18 inches high, the round clip is 0.26 inches high, and the sponge pad is 0.87 inches in diameter. The entire air outlet clip is small and exquisite, easy to carry, and it will not take up a lot of space in the car or room. It is also very good as a decoration, and it is also very convenient to take on travel.

Easy to install This air freshener outlet clamp is easy to install. You only need to open the metal cover of the outlet clamp and put two or three drops of essential oil on the felt pad. Our refined oil bottle has a throttle hole, which allows you to better control the dosage. After dripping the essential oil, cover the metal cover and place the silicone bracket on the air conditioning port. The whole operation is simple and convenient, easy to use, suitable for all people to use.
